name: Rook
public_notice: KeeperDAO (ROOK) has rebranded to Rook (ROOK). For more information please view this press release announcement.

description.en: Rook is an open settlement protocol that leverages the world’s best algorithmic strategists in order to maximize the value of every transaction for protocols, market makers, and traders alike.
